AFN BULLBAR TO SUIT TOYOTA HILUX N80 (2015 – 2018)

AFN bullbar to suit Toyota Hilux N80 (2015 – 2018) available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

The pictured bullbar features;

  • Full Bumper Replacement
  • Rated Recovery Points
  • Dual Antenna Tabs
  • Winch Compatible
  • Hi-Lift Jack Points
  • Fog/Indicator Light Assemblies
  • 6mm Aluminum Bash Plate
  • Matte Black Powder Coated

PLEASE NOTE: The above bar is suited to the wide body Toyota Hilux. Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for this product is approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order. 

CLICK HERE to view the range of products available for your Toyota Hilux!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
